membership:
WWF EPO works with other organisations in various alliances: In the Green10 coalition of the ten biggest EU environmental NGOs in Brussels; as the only environmental NGO of CONCORD, the European confederation of development NGOs; as a member of the Climate Action Network (CAN) Europe, working on climate and energy issues; as part of the sustainable Europe coalition, the Living Rivers Europe coalition, and as a member of the European Habitats Forum (EHF).&#xd;
&#xd;
We also contribute to the following organisations: ECOS, Fédération des Associations Européennes (FAIB), InternsGoPro, Market Advisory Council, North Sea Advisory Council, the Coalition for Energy Savings, and&#xd;
the European Policy Centre.
